        ],
        [
          "As a mortal you you were never happy with who and what you were.  The Spiral Sign is your pack and it was your ideas of change that made the seer Xerxes seek you out.  Xerxes believes a Avatar of Caine will ascend the throne of Caine and as Regent of the Sabbat will lead the sect to victory against the Antediluveans.  You and your pack are constantly searching for the right person, traits, rituals, or materials.  Most simply become vampires, others die in great agony.  None have turned into an Avatar of Caine yet, but it's only a matter of time.  Your own progeny is one such failure.  You believe in the path of metamorphosis and love experimenting on humans, Camarilla, Anarchs, whatever.  In hopes of unlocking thier secrets you torture them night after night seeking to unlock the secrets.  You're not sure if an Avatar of Caine will ever lead the Sabbat, but you are commited to creating one and learning all you can."
